@NODE Registration "Registration"

@{B}                      - - --÷{· @{BG SHADOW}@{APEN 2}  MP3 TAG@{BG HIGHLIGHT}@{APEN 1}ger v1.3  @{BG BACKGROUND} ·}÷-- - -

                         @{B}  ·       @{U}REGISTRATION@{UU}        · @{UB}

   This package is emailware. If you really like it, and use it, then
   you can register MP3Tagger and get your own, personal keyfile. Registering
   will also mean that you will get all the latest updates of MP3Tagger (if you
   want to ofcourse) and we will keep you informed of all the developments.

   To register, just write us an email at @{" faeries@gmx.net " LINK "Authors"} and we
   will send you your keyfile. Once you have received your keyfile, you just have to
   put it in the same directory MP3Tagger is in to enable the registration.

   Note that unregistered versions are NOT crippled in any way - They are fully
   functional! You simply don't have your name in the 'About' requester ;)

   Currently, there is @{b}1@{ub} registered user.

@ENDNODE

