@NODE Requirements "Requirements"

@{B}                      - - --÷{· @{BG SHADOW}@{APEN 2}  MP3 TAG@{BG HIGHLIGHT}@{APEN 1}ger v1.3  @{BG BACKGROUND} ·}÷-- - -

                         @{B}  ·       @{U}REQUIREMENTS@{UU}        · @{UB}

   * An Amiga computer with Kickstart 2.04 or higher
   * About 36 kb of memory

   * The MPEGA.LIBRARY if you want to use MP3 detection and MP3Info displaying.

   * A mouse to use the GUI in an easy way
