   When the genre is not specified, you are advised to use the value 255 (-1), which
   is commonly regarded as the 'undefinied genre' value.


      --------- Footnotes ----------

   (1) The Genre information was taken from the MP3Info developper docs.
       Additional Genres were taken from the MPTool program.
       WinAMP genres were taken from the AmTAGID3 program.
   (2) The MP3 TAG structure was hacked out by us (loads of experimenting)
       This is not a lame copy from any of the other docs!
   (3) More information on decoding MPEG audio files can be found on
       @{b}www.mp3.com@{ub}

